00:09:24.560 --> 00:09:26.240
'Bagaimana kamu
bisa begitu kuat, Uruvi?'

00:09:27.000 --> 00:09:29.520
'Meskipun Karn marah dan benci'

00:09:29.560 --> 00:09:32.840
